<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<!--
  TASK-69 — Settings screen chrome (hand-written UI copy, resolved via
  StringResolver -> AndroidStringResolver -> plain Android string resources,
  same mechanism as strings.xml / strings_preset_task120.xml; this app does
  NOT use Compose Multiplatform Resources for StringResolver despite the
  port's doc comment mentioning it — see Spec015Module.kt binding).

  Row/category content comes from LocalizedResources instead — see
  strings_preset_task120.xml `settings.row.*` / `settings.category.*`.

  `settings_title` reuses the pre-existing key in strings.xml (same value,
  original owner of the string) rather than redeclaring it here.
-->
